      • withId

        IReadExecutable<T> withId(IIdType theId)
        Search using an ID. Note that even if theId contains a base URL it will be ignored in favour of the base url for the given client. If you want to specify an absolute URL including a base and have that base used instead, use withUrl(IIdType)
